<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 16:10:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>双倍乐趣？ 《死侍与金刚狼》看起来只不过是漫威的一场现金抢夺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/double-the-fun-deadpool-wolverine-seems-little-more-than-a-marvel-cash-grab/00000190-f88e-df0c-ab98-ffbf81950000</link><description>漫威最新的超级英雄电影感觉像是在营销会议而不是编剧室中创作的，而《龙卷风》则缺乏前作的乐趣。至少《Longlegs》是一款令人不安、扣人心弦的手表</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 15:52:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/double-the-fun-deadpool-wolverine-seems-little-more-than-a-marvel-cash-grab/00000190-f88e-df0c-ab98-ffbf81950000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，以色列军队在加沙南部深入推进；据报道20人死亡，数千人逃离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/israeli-forces-reportedly-advance-deeper-in-south-gaza-20-reported-killed-thousands-flee/00000190-f9d8-d5ef-a5fe-fbde87be0000</link><description>随着以色列撤离命令促使更多人离开加沙中部和南部，以色列坦克开进了汗尤尼斯。以色列国防军表示，一名军官和一名士兵在加沙南部的战斗中受重伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 15:41:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/israeli-forces-reportedly-advance-deeper-in-south-gaza-20-reported-killed-thousands-flee/00000190-f9d8-d5ef-a5fe-fbde87be0000</guid></item><item><title>“笨拙”但沉重：真主党在迈季代勒沙姆斯发射伊朗制造的火箭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/dumb-but-heavy-the-iranian-made-rocket-hezbollah-launched-at-majdal-shams/00000190-f91e-d987-a59c-f9bf20fd0000</link><description>Falaq 1于20世纪90年代在伊朗研制，旨在为军队提供重型火箭炮，能够打击掩体和其他目标，在叙利亚内战期间，它被真主党和叙利亚军队使用。自一月份以来，真主党已向以色列发射了数十次火箭</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 14:38:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/dumb-but-heavy-the-iranian-made-rocket-hezbollah-launched-at-majdal-shams/00000190-f91e-d987-a59c-f9bf20fd0000</guid></item><item><title>如果美国不否决对以色列的制裁怎么办？法律专家称“这是世界末日”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-if-the-u-s-doesnt-veto-sanctions-against-israel-its-the-end-of-the-world/00000190-f95b-d667-ad9f-fddb9f940000</link><description>犹太人民政策研究所副所长舒基·弗里德曼表示，对定居者实施制裁的影响不仅限于约旦河西岸，而且已经在削弱以色列的国际合法性。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 14:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-if-the-u-s-doesnt-veto-sanctions-against-israel-its-the-end-of-the-world/00000190-f95b-d667-ad9f-fddb9f940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的德鲁兹社区解释说</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-druze-community-in-israel-explained/00000188-8c42-d3c4-afec-9ed397020000</link><description>以色列德鲁兹人正在哀悼在黎巴嫩火箭弹袭击戈兰高地期间丧生的 11 名儿童。这个紧密团结的社区在以色列军事和社会中发挥着关键作用，但在这些问题上也存在分歧。谁是德鲁兹人，他们与中东各地社区的关系如何，最近的战争对他们有何影响？</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 14:05:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-druze-community-in-israel-explained/00000188-8c42-d3c4-afec-9ed397020000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列与哈马斯人质停火协议将包括外国人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-israel-hamas-hostage-cease-fire-deal-would-include-foreign-nationals/00000190-f8b1-d901-abd6-feb9c0ed0000</link><description>据以色列军方称，有 10 名外国人在加沙地带被扣为人质，其中 7 人还活着。 ■ 警方还在调查一名自 10 月 7 日起失踪的泰国公民的案件</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 11:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-israel-hamas-hostage-cease-fire-deal-would-include-foreign-nationals/00000190-f8b1-d901-abd6-feb9c0ed0000</guid></item><item><title>一位面临所有困难的跨巴勒斯坦妇女</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/the-story-of-a-trans-palestinian-woman-who-had-all-the-odds-stacked-against-her/00000190-f8b0-df0c-ab98-ffbb1a280000</link><description>纪录片《她的名字叫泽哈瓦》去年在海法电影节上获得了著名奖项，但战争意味着它必须等待才能重返大银幕</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 10:22:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/the-story-of-a-trans-palestinian-woman-who-had-all-the-odds-stacked-against-her/00000190-f8b0-df0c-ab98-ffbb1a280000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部11名儿童被杀，但内塔尼亚胡并不着急</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-killed-in-northern-israel-but-as-far-as-netanyahus-concerned-theres-no-rush/00000190-f838-d541-adbc-f9f844a40000</link><description>一个正在“七条战线”作战并出国旅行一周（包括一次特别的周末停留）的国家的元首根本不是一个领导人。他会的</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 08:13:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-killed-in-northern-israel-but-as-far-as-netanyahus-concerned-theres-no-rush/00000190-f838-d541-adbc-f9f844a40000</guid></item><item><title>数千人参加以色列北部真主党火箭袭击中丧生的儿童和青少年的葬礼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-and-teens-killed-in-north-israel-rocket-strike-to-be-laid-to-rest/00000190-f7ed-d469-a39d-f7ff90670000</link><description>10 名遇难者被埋葬在真主党火箭周六袭击的 Majdal Shams ■ 另一名遇难者被安葬在恩钦亚 ■ 28 人仍在医院接受治疗</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 06:37:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-and-teens-killed-in-north-israel-rocket-strike-to-be-laid-to-rest/00000190-f7ed-d469-a39d-f7ff90670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/00000190-f7ca-d469-a39d-f7df6c950000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布一周前被反坦克火力击伤的尤纳坦·阿哈龙·格林布拉特中士死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 05:38:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/00000190-f7ca-d469-a39d-f7df6c950000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列“肯定”会在黎巴嫩进行报复，避免袭击贝鲁特的谈判正在进行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-live/u-s-condemns-horrific-attack-reportedly-highly-concerned-over-all-out-war/00000190-f724-d469-a39d-f7b7cff70000</link><description>以色列国防军：两名士兵在加沙南部受重伤 ■ 真主党火箭袭击以色列 Majdal Shams 造成 12 名儿童和青少年死亡 ■ 以色列国防军宣布，以色列士兵在上周加沙战斗中受伤死亡 ■ 黎巴嫩报告：以色列在加沙以北发动一系列袭击提尔和黎巴嫩南部 ■ 伊朗外交部警告黎巴嫩境内任何新的“以色列冒险” ■ 以色列外交部发言人：“真主党是对周六大屠杀明确负责的实体”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 02:40:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-live/u-s-condemns-horrific-attack-reportedly-highly-concerned-over-all-out-war/00000190-f724-d469-a39d-f7b7cff70000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在华盛顿的胜利并不能抵消他的惨重损失</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wins-in-washington-dont-cancel-out-his-heavy-losses/00000190-f66b-d541-adbc-fffb226c0000</link><description>尽管内塔尼亚胡在椭圆形办公室合影并在国会获得掌声，但许多关键问题仍未解决——尤其是人质交易——并且与卡马拉·哈里斯爆发了激烈的争执</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 23:49:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wins-in-washington-dont-cancel-out-his-heavy-losses/00000190-f66b-d541-adbc-fffb226c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党比以往任何时候都更接近全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-risks-full-scale-escalation-with-hezbollah-while-still-wrangling-on-gaza-front/00000190-f5cb-dda7-a9f7-f7ff03d80000</link><description>周六，以色列在北部玩的俄罗斯轮盘赌在马贾勒沙姆斯失败了，当时真主党对以色列对其特工的袭击做出了回应。由于坚持延长华盛顿之行，内塔尼亚胡总理只能远程参加防务磋商</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 21:59:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-risks-full-scale-escalation-with-hezbollah-while-still-wrangling-on-gaza-front/00000190-f5cb-dda7-a9f7-f7ff03d80000</guid></item><item><title>为内塔尼亚胡欢呼的参议员和国会议员感到羞耻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/shame-on-the-senators-and-congressmen-who-cheered-netanyahu/00000190-f554-dda7-a9f7-f777bd370000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 21:33:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/shame-on-the-senators-and-congressmen-who-cheered-netanyahu/00000190-f554-dda7-a9f7-f777bd370000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：真主党将付出前所未有的代价；最高部长呼吁暗杀纳斯鲁拉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/netanyahu-hezbollah-will-pay-unprecedented-price-top-minister-calls-to-kill-nasrallah/00000190-f5ca-d8b8-a59a-fdde66be0000</link><description>真主党否认对以色列北部德鲁兹城镇发动致命袭击负责，该袭击造成 11 名儿童和青少年死亡。白宫谴责这起“可怕”的袭击，而以色列北部当地领导人要求立即采取军事回应</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 20:57:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/netanyahu-hezbollah-will-pay-unprecedented-price-top-minister-calls-to-kill-nasrallah/00000190-f5ca-d8b8-a59a-fdde66be0000</guid></item><item><title>“孩子们来玩，爆炸将他们撕成碎片”：目击者讲述了令人痛心的 Majdal Shams 袭击事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/children-came-to-play-and-an-explosion-shredded-them-to-pieces/00000190-f596-d8b8-a59a-fd9e0e080000</link><description>到达造成 11 名儿童和青少年死亡的罢工现场的 Majdal Shams 和附近村庄的居民报告说，爆炸发生在警报响起几秒钟后。地上有受伤和死亡的儿童。这让我想起了 10 月 7 日。”一位居民说道</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 20:30:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/children-came-to-play-and-an-explosion-shredded-them-to-pieces/00000190-f596-d8b8-a59a-fd9e0e080000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩火箭袭击以色列戈兰高地，造成 11 名儿童和青少年死亡；以色列国防军指责真主党</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/11-children-teens-killed-and-dozens-wounded-in-rocket-strike-on-majdal-shams/00000190-f54a-d298-a592-fd7bffe80000</link><description>以色列医疗部门表示，此次袭击袭击了一个正在玩耍的儿童足球场，共有 29 人受伤。以色列国防军指责真主党发动了这次袭击，此前以色列对四名特工发动了袭击。现场的一名医生回忆道，“所有受害者都是 8 至 14 岁的儿童，都穿着运动服”</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 19:09:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/11-children-teens-killed-and-dozens-wounded-in-rocket-strike-on-majdal-shams/00000190-f54a-d298-a592-fd7bffe80000</guid></item><item><title>法院以“危害安全”为由延长半岛电视台在以色列的广播禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/court-extends-al-jazeera-broadcasting-ban-in-israel-citing-harm-to-security/00000190-f54f-d541-adbc-fdffd24b0000</link><description>该禁令是根据议会五月通过的一项法律发布的，该法律允许半岛电视台停止从以色列进行广播。法官表示，他已经看到证据证明该电视台播放的内容煽动恐怖袭击</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 18:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/court-extends-al-jazeera-broadcasting-ban-in-israel-citing-harm-to-security/00000190-f54f-d541-adbc-fdffd24b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队无人机袭击约旦河西岸纳布卢斯巴勒斯坦武装分子，17岁青年被打死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-drone-targets-palestinian-militants-in-west-banks-nablus-17-year-old-killed/00000190-f527-d45d-a5b3-ffaf9d060000</link><description>军方表示，纳布卢斯巴拉塔难民营的袭击目标是武装武装分子，造成一人死亡、多人受伤。以色列安全部门消息人士称，这是对当天早上针对以色列国防军士兵的枪击事件的回应</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 17:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-drone-targets-palestinian-militants-in-west-banks-nablus-17-year-old-killed/00000190-f527-d45d-a5b3-ffaf9d060000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事，第 295 天：来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹在以色列北部迈季代勒沙姆斯造成 9 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-295-rocket-fire-from-lebanon-kills-nine-in-north-israels-majdal-shams/00000190-f4af-dda7-a9f7-f7bfb5bd0000</link><description>戈兰高地 Majdal Shams 镇遭火箭弹袭击，造成 9 名以色列人死亡，伤亡人数最多的是儿童和青少年 ■ 巴勒斯坦人称，以色列国防军的袭击导致汗尤尼斯 (Khan Yunis) 23 人死亡，代尔巴拉学校 (Deir al-Balah) 至少 30 人死亡；以色列国防军：哈马斯利用学校作为指挥中心 ■ 以色列代表团下周前往罗马进行协议谈判 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在检查站受伤；巴勒斯坦卫生部门消息来源：随后的以色列国防军无人机袭击和约旦河西岸冲突导致 17 岁儿童死亡、28 人受伤 ■ 以下是战争进入 295 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 17:16:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-295-rocket-fire-from-lebanon-kills-nine-in-north-israels-majdal-shams/00000190-f4af-dda7-a9f7-f7bfb5bd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>